messages.messageBody:
I do not get to post for another week!!!!! However in light of
enlightenment I will give you all of my knowledge, which is next to
nothing. Warhammer is a role playing boardgame. Very complex from my
understanding. And those action figures.. Better known as Dark Eldar
Warriors are part of the play. We however had a mishap with my sons.
My daughter borrowed them several year ago for a project she did in
sixth grade. THe kids in her middle school stole them. I was
thrilled when I saw Deb looking for a good home.My son who will be
20 in February will get some guys back.
Kathleen
PS>>> I have enjoyed reading everyones posts..








--- In UnschoolingDiscussion@yahoogroups.com, Deborah Lewis
